menu "School Bell Configuration"

    config BSP_IO_EXPANDER_I2C_ADDR
        hex "CH32V003 IO Expander I2C address"
        default 0x20
        help
            I2C address of the CH32V003 IO expander on the Waveshare
            ESP32-S3-Touch-LCD-4 board. The default 0x20 matches the
            address used by the board. The upstream component default
            is 0x24.

endmenu
